    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes optional extensions to Simple Two-way Active Measurement Protocol (STAMP) that enable measurement of performance metrics.  The document also defines a STAMP Test Session Identifier and thus updates RFC 8762.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
